    dc:description "Figs 1-7: tergite, sternite of the male genital segment, aedeagus of Pachycorynus helvus nov.sp. (1- 3) (bar scale: 0,1 mm); head and pronoum (bar scale: 1 mm), labrum, tergite, sternite of the male genital segment of Thyreocephalus macrophallus nov.sp. (4-7)." ;
